import React from 'react';
import styled from 'styled-components';

const LoginPageContainer = styled.div`
  display: flex;
  top: 90px;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  width: 612px;
  height: 753px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  border-radius: 0rem 1.25rem 1.25rem 0rem;
  background-color: #CFDFF3;
`;

const LoginPage = () => {
  return (
    <LoginPageLight1>
      <LogInWindow>
        <Right>
          <Right1 src={Right1Image} loading='lazy' alt={"Right"}/>
          <InsideRight>
          </InsideRight>
          <CreateAccount>
            {`Create Account`}
          </CreateAccount>
          <ForgotPassword>
            {`Forgot Password?`}
          </ForgotPassword>
          <Submit>
            <Submit1 src={Submit1Image} loading='lazy' alt={"Submit"}/>
            <Frame>
              <ClipPathGroup src={ClipPathGroupImage} loading='lazy' alt={"Clip path group"}/>
            </Frame>
          </Submit>
          <Password>
            <Password1>
            </Password1>
            <Password2>
              {`password`}
            </Password2>
          </Password>
          <Username>
            <Username1>
            </Username1>
            <Frame1>
              <Username2>
                {`username`}
              </Username2>
            </Frame1>
          </Username>
          <Login>
            {`Login`}
          </Login>
          <IndiaPost src={IndiaPostImage} loading='lazy' alt={"IndiaPost"}/>
        </Right>
        <Left>
          <Left1 src={Left1Image} loading='lazy' alt={"Left"}/>
          <Road src={RoadImage} loading='lazy' alt={"Road"}/>
          <Truck src={TruckImage} loading='lazy' alt={"Truck"}/>
          <Men src={MenImage} loading='lazy' alt={"Men"}/>
        </Left>
      </LogInWindow>
      <LightMode>
        <Rectangle1>
        </Rectangle1>
        <Frame2>
          <ClipPathGroup1 src={ClipPathGroup1Image} loading='lazy' alt={"Clip path group"}/>
        </Frame2>
      </LightMode>
      <Q75Years1 src={Q75Years1Image} loading='lazy' alt={"75 years 1"}/>
      <Navbar>
        <NavbarBackground src={NavbarBackgroundImage} loading='lazy' alt={"Navbar-Background"}/>
        <Logo src={LogoImage} loading='lazy' alt={"Logo"}/>
        <LeftText>
          <English>
            {`DakGhar Niryat Kendra -  Customer Portal`}
          </English>
          <Hindi>
            {`Mkd?kj fu;
kZr dsanz & xkzgd iksVZy`}
          </Hindi>
        </LeftText>
      </Navbar>
      <Screenshot20230921At src={Screenshot20230921AtImage} loading='lazy' alt={"Screenshot 2023-09-21 at 10.37 Background Removed 1"}/>
      <Q75Years2 src={Q75Years2Image} loading='lazy' alt={"75 years 2"}/>
    </LoginPageLight1>);

  }

export default LoginPage;
